    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And before we left the place, we-- we made a thing-- we-- we decided when something happen, when we was every time on the run, we should come in-- in one village is a woods.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there is a doctor with a family stays there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We find out this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And everybody-- what-- wherever we're running, we should get-- to come together for the-- in this place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "For this place, what we was, it about 25 miles to the other one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] was sitting through the day in the bush and then the night they go there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When the Germans start shooting on us to the day-- because the Germans came to the-- to the farmers to collecting bread for the army and some other things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's the time they was in the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In fact, when they-- when they go and tell a Jew-- when they see a Jew and they tell the Germans, the Germans give you a pound of sugar.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
